      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_7859470012861470303.png",
                "id": "talent28642",
                "key": "千金擲",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "千金擲"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">璇璣屏</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">璇璣屏</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方出戰角色受到至少為2的傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/2a1c2baa706dfc49f86033be36f170e9_214705509797190541.png",
                "id": "talent16351",
                "key": "璇璣屏",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "璇璣屏"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成6點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>；如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">璇璣屏</span>在場，就使此傷害+2。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">璇璣屏</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出戰角色受到至少為2的傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/55dfd3944aa4091c2684c17412739558_7473569786414452379.png",
                "id": "talent41642",
                "key": "天權崩玉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "天權崩玉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_4554621203137607680.png",
